                        <div class="modal-body career-talk text-center">
                        	<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">x</button>
                            <h1>Career Talk</h1>
                            <p>Talk to your chosen advisor about anything and everything related to your career.</p>
                            <h3>STEP 1</h3>
                            <p>Send your query to the advisor when booking a session with them and connect on the session day through your chosen mode of communication</p>
                            <h3>STEP 2</h3>
                            <p>Send a follow up mail after your session to clear up any remaining doubts</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                
            <div class="col-md-2 col-xs-3 text-center service-link">
            	<a data-target="#interview" data-toggle="modal" style="cursor:pointer">
                	<img width="100" alt="" src="assets/img/WebMail/HomePage/Panel_2_Icon_5.png"><br> Mock Interview
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="modal fade" id="interview" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
                    <div class="modal-content">
                        <div class="modal-body mock-interview text-center">
                        	<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">x</button>
                            <h1>Mock Interview</h1>
                            <p>Our advisors have got years of experience in taking interviews in their fields so they know just the things you need to ace it.</p>
                            <h3>STEP 1</h3>
                            <p>Send in your Interview details and Resume with your session request</p>
                            <h3>STEP 2</h3>
                            <p>Connect with your advisor on the session day for a practice interview designed specially keeping your requirements in mind</p>
                            <h3>STEP 3</h3>
                            <p>Get an in-depth analysis of your performance post the session. You can also send a follow-up mail to clear any doubts.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-2 col-xs-3 text-center service-link">
            	<a data-target="#resume" data-toggle="modal" style="cursor:pointer">
                	<img width="100" alt="" src="assets/img/WebMail/HomePage/Panel_2_Icon_3.png"><br> Resume Critique
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="modal fade" id="resume" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
                    <div class="modal-content">
                        <div class="modal-body resume text-center">
                        	<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">x</button>
                            <h1>Resume Critique</h1>
                            <p>Headhunters, recruiter, employers. We've got them all to help you build that sought after resume and land that interview shortlist!</p>
                            <h3>STEP 1</h3>
                            <p>Send in details of your targeted profile and updated Resume with your session request to the advisor.</p>
                            <h3>STEP 2</h3>
                            <p>Receive a written analysis of your CV on various parameters before your session date.</p>
                            <h3>STEP 3</h3>
                            <p>Connect with your advisor on the session day for thorough analysis of your Resume and profile.</p>
                            <h3>STEP 4</h3>
                            <p>Send a follow-up mail after your session in case of any doubts.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
